<br>
We are the purest of all the spell casting classes.  We rely on no pet, no heals, no FD.  Our class relies on our wits, knowing what to cast, when to cast, to bring down a mob, no other class compares.<br>
<br>
Personally, I have no burning desire to play my alts on an ongoing basis, because whenever I do, they come up short compared to the sheer enjoyment of playing a wizardress<br>
